    <item>
      <title>欧亚集团称印度将从联盟对莫迪的制衡中受益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/modi-s-new-coalition-government-is-good-for-india-eurasia-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧亚集团总裁伊恩·布雷默周四表示，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的新联合政府是这个世界第一人口大国最好的选举结果，并指出分权结构需要更多的共识建设。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/modi-s-new-coalition-government-is-good-for-india-eurasia-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 05:37:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪期待连任后与台湾建立更紧密关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/modi-looks-forward-to-closer-ties-with-taiwan-after-reelection</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪在社交媒体上直接回应台湾新当选总统，表示期待与台湾建立更紧密的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/modi-looks-forward-to-closer-ties-with-taiwan-after-reelection</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 04:37:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列称袭击了位于加沙一所学校的哈马斯设施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/israel-says-conducts-deadly-airstrike-at-gaza-school-complex</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列军方称，对位于加沙地带一所学校建筑内的哈马斯营地进行了空袭，消灭了参与 10 月 7 日针对以色列平民发动致命袭击的武装分子。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/israel-says-conducts-deadly-airstrike-at-gaza-school-complex</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 04:05:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
